UPSERT finding:doc_docs_per_object_quad_spec_md_the_single_most_important_new_re_finding_in_this SET statement='The single most important new RE finding in this spec (and a contradiction with the existing Oracle\'s recorded conclusion): loc_8c033d78 / loc_8c033e90 is NOT load-time-only. It is driven per character, every in-match frame by the render driver loc_8c03dcba → loop loc_8c03dd6c (6× stride 0x5A4 from 0x8C268340). The "fires once at frame 2568" note in maplecast_oracle_hook.cpp:50-56 is wrong, OR the', status='inferred', confidence='doc', source_file='docs/PER-OBJECT-QUAD-SPEC.md', section='0. TL;DR of the chosen mechanism';
