UPSERT finding:doc_memory_reference_mvc2_effects_bank_md_2026_06_07_re_finding_mvc2_sh4_re_expert_mvc2 SET statement='2026-06-07 RE finding (mvc2-sh4-re-expert): MVC2 has no separate effect sprite_id namespace. Every render object (body, cape, projectile, hitspark) runs through the same quad emitter loc_8c033e90 and resolves its texture from a per-object GFX base pointer at owner+0x15C (Dat_GFX1), indexed by part_idx — NOT by sprite_id. So shared effects\' sprite_ids COLLIDE numerically with per-character part ind', status='inferred', confidence='doc', source_file='memory/reference_mvc2_effects_bank.md', section='';
