UPSERT finding:doc_memory_reference_mvc2_slot_table_drawlist_md_implemented_as_readalldrawn_in_reference_key SET statement='Implemented as readAllDrawn() in [[reference_key_files]] core/network/maplecast_gamestate.cpp, gated MAPLECAST_OBJS_SLOTTABLE. Confirmed: supers now render. Open refinements: placement/z-order (ship the layer byte; client z-sort) and object smoothness (client interpolates the body via velocity but draws anonymous OBJS objects at raw per-frame positions). The owner-scan (legacy) and head-list walke', status='confirmed', confidence='doc', source_file='memory/reference_mvc2_slot_table_drawlist.md', section='';
