UPSERT finding:doc_memory_reference_mvc2_wire_gaps_md_2_char_0x151_renderextra_selects_the_additive SET statement='2. char+0x151 RenderExtra — selects the additive effect/aura/super-overlay layer (Storm: 12=Lightning Storm, 39=Lightning Attack, 64=flight aura). Copied by anim tick loc_8c034dee (bank03:11567). Drives the multi-part super-field overlays we were filtering out — likely a cleaner path than STAF for supers. The body sprite alone can\'t render these. CORRECTION (2026-06-07 disasm trace → docs/MVC2-REC', status='confirmed', confidence='doc', source_file='memory/reference_mvc2_wire_gaps.md', section='';
